description:
Enoch Moore asks Green Lantern to locate his long-missing son Ray Moore. Alan soon discovers the young man is a member of a crtiminal gang led by Killer Dill. He wants to help Ray escape a life of crime.

What he doesn't find out until later is that the Moores are in league with each other. They want Alan to take out Dill for them. Leaving the leadership position open for Ray.
name: Spring Time for Doiby

description:
This comic has 4 different covers with different characters featured.

Just in time for Casper's 60th anniversary, Ardden Entertainment proudly debuts Casper And The Supernaturals, an all-new take on the world's most famous ghost and his two friends, Wendy the Witch and Hot Stuff! There is a city within New York City known as Spooky Town, but most humans are unable to see it. Within this city live the Supernaturals, the ghosts, goblins, demons and witches of the world. When an ancient entity known only as the Volbragg threatens both New York and Spooky Town, Casper and his friends are forced to band together and defeat an unimaginable evil!
name: Casper and the Spectrals

description:
The Future is here! From Dynamite, writer Scott Beatty and artist Carlos Rafael comes the all-new adventures of Buck Rogers!

In "The Space Beneath: Parts 2 (of 2)" Buck has gone underground on the trail of his captured ship and what he has found there is shocking and amazing. In the conclusion, he must make a momentous decision that will affect the underground world...
name: The Space Beneath: Part 2: The Fire Down Below

description: The bloody conclusion of the horror series of the year has too much violence to fit in a normal comic, so this final issue is super-sized! There is nothing left to do but for Cindy and the last of her friends to take the battle to the Crossed. It doesn?t go well. Garth Ennis takes no prisoners and offers no hope in the most intense book of his career! Nothing is going right, but this is no fairy tale -- there are no magic cures on the horizon. When civilization crumbles in one terrifying moment; when people are gleefully breaking into unthinkable acts of violence all around you; when everyone you love has died screaming in agony: What do you do? There is no help. There is no hope. There is no escape. There are only the Crossed. This stomach-churning vision is brought to vivid by his partner in crime Jacen Burrows. This nihilistic ninth issue is available with a Regular or Wraparound cover by Burrows as well as a rare Red Crossed Edition by Burrows.

The villainous Commander Borf has attacked Ace with the 'Infanto Ray,' a weapon that transforms him into an adolescent version of himself, and kidnaps his girlfriend Kimberly.

It is up to Dexter - Ace's younger incarnation - to rescue Kimberly and prevent Borf using the Infanto Ray to conquer Earth. Space Ace dominated the video arcades and now see it dominate your local retailer!

The stakes get higher as Donald, in his new role as Double Duck, is drawn further into the Agencys world of shadowy intrigue and danger! This is Donald Duck like youve never seen him, as only BOOM! Kids can deliver.

Re-qui-em (noun): A song or hymn of mourning composed or performed as a memorial to the departed. With the catastrophes wrought by Ultimatum, does this spell the end for the the Ultimate Universe? Spider-Man has fallen and the Ultimate Universe will never be the same! Original series artist Mark Bagley returns for a special story celebrating the heroism of everyone's favorite webslinger. Then in X-Men, the surviving members of the team say goodbye to their loved ones, pay homage to their memory, and try to figure out what happens next. And in Fantastic Four, find out if the first family can continue on in the wake of Ultimatum's devastating events.

Collects Ultimatum: Spider-Man Requiem, Fantastic Four Requiem, and X-Men Requiem.
name: HC/TPB

description: An exciting new chapter in the Legend of Isis series begins here with Part One of the 'Rise of Darkness' story arc. Recovering from the events of the 'God War,' the last thing Isis needs is for more trouble to come her way. Her evil brother Set makes a play for Isis' life by awaking the God of Darkness Apophis. Can Isis survive this onslaught of evil?

When Professor Farnsworth's latest invention gives Bender the ability to fly, the misanthropic robot finds that he has the power to save the world. But with great power comes great responsibility, and Bender wants no part of it.
name: Chitty Chitty Bend Bend

description: There's a new Dragon in Salem. She can freeze the blood in your veins. She can make your flesh crack off your bones like ice with her breath. Salem, Massachusetts is under a deadly cold spell this winter. To go outside is a death sentence, and Tarot stands alone to take on her icy bite!
name: The Dragon Witch of Winter
